name: Medicatons_Hyperlipidemia
title: medicatons_Hyperlipidemia
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set intends to capture generic and brand codes for Hyperlipidemia recommendable medications (Statins, Ezetimibe, PCSK9i)),(Data Element Scope: DRUG_CLASS_MEMBERS: INDICATION: Hyperlipidemia),(Inclusion Criteria: All generics (with different strengths) and brands (with different strengths) for Hyperlipidemia Medications),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes Bile Acid Sequestrants, Fibrates, Niacin and Omega-3 fatty acids)
